name: monthly-project-showcase-october
title: Monthly Project Showcase
shortDescription: Form teams to build a project around a selected theme and show it off the following month!
longDescription: The Monthly Project Showcase is a monthly meetup for club members interested in gaining experience working in a team, as well as building up their portfolio! Each month, participants get together to vote on a theme for the month, form teams to work with, and build awesome projects to showcase the following month.
